<li><strong>Should cities invest in weather stations or climate studies? Why?</strong><br /><em>Hint:</em> Think about planning for floods vs. daily rain forecasts.</li>
<li><strong>How can individuals contribute to recording local climate data?</strong><br /><em>Hint:</em> Simple tools like rain gauges and diaries can help.</li>
</ol>
